text: Ærest up of crægean on fulan riðe.
Of þam gebyhte andlang hagan oð cyninges healh.
Þanon andlang hagan ut on crægean.
Of ðam burnan andlang hagan on casincgstræt east andlang stræte on scoffoces sæ.
Þanon norð andlang stræte oð lytlanlea.
Þanon east andlang mearce oð enede mere suð rihte of ðam mere to burnes stede.
Andlang stræte on þone calewan telgan.
Helfreðingdenn, Hunbealdinghola, Frumesingleah, Burnes stedesdenn, Heanyfre.
Þæs gemære is on easthealfe spachrycg.
